text: Chris Hanson (born 12 December 1990 in New York) is an American professional squash player. As of July 2018, he was ranked number 60 in the world. ==References== ==External links== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:American male squash players Category:Dartmouth Big Green men's squash players Category:Squash players at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games medalists in squash Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for the United States
